These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: fanta, milk, coffee, juice
Hobby: magic-tricks, skydiving, video-games, rock-climbing
1. Beverage:milk is between Beverage:fanta and Hobby:skydiving##2
2. Beverage:milk is on the left or right of Hobby:magic-tricks##3
3. Beverage:milk is somewhere between Beverage:juice and Beverage:fanta##7
4. Hobby:skydiving is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:juice is on the right of Hobby:video-games##1
6. Hobby:skydiving is somewhere to the left of Hobby:magic-tricks##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | coffee | juice       | milk | fanta        |
| Hobby      | video-games  | skydiving | rock-climbing        | magic-tricks |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
Pet: rabbit, turtle, lizard, goldfish
Sport: skiing, water-polo, handball, snowboarding
1. Sport:snowboarding is somewhere between Sport:handball and Pet:lizard##7
2. Pet:goldfish is somewhere to the left of Pet:rabbit##5
3. Pet:goldfish is somewhere to the right of Sport:snowboarding##5
4. Pet:turtle is on the left of Pet:goldfish##1
5. Sport:snowboarding is between Sport:handball and Sport:water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | lizard | turtle       | goldfish         | rabbit     |
| Sport   | water-polo   | snowboarding | handball | skiing |

