.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Hobby: sudoku, filmmaking, baking, singing
Sport: basketball, swimming, snowboarding, handball
1. Sport:handball is on the far left or far right##3
2. Hobby:sudoku is somewhere between Sport:swimming and Hobby:singing##7
3. Hobby:baking == Sport:handball##1
4. Sport:snowboarding is on the left of Sport:handball##1
5. Hobby:filmmaking is on the left of Sport:basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | sudoku | singing       | baking |
| Sport   | swimming      | basketball   | snowboarding | handball  |

